Definition: written or spoken) that persuades someone to accept something untrue or undesirable
Example: they tried to sell me a bill of goods about a secondhand car
Synonyms: misrepresentation, communication, written, or, spoken, that, persuades, someone, to, accept, something, untrue, undesirable, they, tried, sell, me, a, bill, of, goods, about, secondhand, car
Category: noun.communication
